# HEYDAY client

- Pages: `client/src/pages/` · components: `client/src/components/`
- Auth: `ProtectedRoute` + `credentials: 'include'` on all `/api` fetches
- Shell: `DashboardLayout` (Sidebar + TopNav); `marginLeft` from `SidebarContext`
- Shared: `Icon`, `DateText`, `format.js`, `TeamAvatar`

Add routes in `App.jsx` + nav in `Sidebar.jsx`.

## Sidebar

- `SidebarContext` — `collapsed`, `sidebarWidth` (260 | 72), `sidebar-collapsed-v1`
- Nav: Team Hub, Task Hub (+ nested My Transaction/Admin/Projects), CRM, Revenue, Transactions, Marketing, Feedback
- Task Hub `NavLink` `end={taskHub}`; Transactions link uses `resolveTransactionsSidebarLink()`
- Logo: `import heydayLogo from '../assets/heyday-logo.png'`

## Favicon

- Assets: `client/public/favicon.png`, `favicon-32.png`, `apple-touch-icon.png`
- Linked in `client/index.html` — Vite serves `/public` at root

## Agent scope

- `AgentScopeProvider` in `App.jsx`
- `AgentScopeToggle` / `AgentScopeBadge` in TopNav
- `appendAgentScope(params, scope)` on fetch URLs for transactions, revenue, marketing, tasks

## Transactions

- **List** `TransactionsList.jsx` — filter tabs, sortable columns, KPI row, pagination
- Current Listings: columns include **Expiration** (`important_date`), not Agent
- Create modal step 1: `validateCreateTransaction` (address fields only)
- List state: `transactionsListPath.js`, `TransactionsNavTracker`, sessionStorage `transactions-list-view-v1`
- **Workspace** `TransactionManager.jsx` → `TransactionWorkspace.jsx`
  - Views: details, checklist, activity
  - Checklist: compact rows, `font-medium` titles, complete = strikethrough (no COMPLETED label)
  - Panel: `min-h-[32rem] max-h-[calc(100vh-12.5rem)]`; click row → detail sidebar
  - Delete transaction: show alert on failure (`deleteTransaction` returns `{ ok, error }`)

## Task Hub

- `TaskHubTabs.jsx` — Transaction Tasks | Admin Tasks | Projects
- `TaskHubPersonHeader.jsx` — back link, avatar, title, optional filter children
- `displayTaskTitle()` from `taskDisplay.js` for calendar chips
- `TaskCalendarView.jsx` — `.calendar-grid` 7 cols Sun–Sat

## Feedback

- `HubFeedback.jsx` — `DashboardLayout` title "Feedback"
- `HubDocList.jsx` — fetch `/api/hub-docs?section=feedback`, inline edit, Enter adds bullet

## Checklist editor

- `ChecklistEditor.jsx` — textarea title, nickname, default assignee select, timing row
- Save sends `calendar_nickname` + `default_role` to API

## Marketing calendar

- `MarketingDayEvents` order: Social → Tasks → Milestones
- `PlatformQuotasRow` — weekly goals; collapsible via localStorage
- Double-click empty day cell → `MarketingPostModal`; platforms = `filterPlatforms`
- Birthday pins + `MonthBirthdaysModal`; social `done` = crossed-out chips

## Project dashboard

- `UserProjectDashboard.jsx` — 3-column: projects | pending todos | done todos
- Components in `client/src/components/projects/`

## Calendar CSS

- `.calendar-grid` in `index.css` — `repeat(7, 1fr)`; header must be 7 columns
- Avoid `overflow-hidden` on calendar wrapper if it clips Saturday column
